sourcesContent: import*as e from"jose";class t{static parse(e){try{return new t(e)}catch(e){return null}}get subject(){return this._decoded.sub}get expiration(){return this._decoded.exp}get issuer(){return this._decoded.iss}get audience(){return this._decoded.aud}isExpired(e=0){return Date.now()>=1e3*(this.expiration-e)}constructor(t){this.value=t,this._decoded=e.decodeJwt(t)}}export{t as Token};
